404
00:22:08,009 --> 00:22:10,470
Don't worry.
I think I can handle Roddy Gerber.

405
00:22:11,512 --> 00:22:13,915
I'm just warning you.
He's a very tough guy.

406
00:22:14,208 --> 00:22:17,460
I'd like to see him try something,
we'll see how tough he is.

407
00:22:17,709 --> 00:22:18,709
Whatever.

408
00:22:25,496 --> 00:22:26,514
<i>Roddy Gerber?</i>

409
00:22:26,873 --> 00:22:28,137
